PrecisAppointment of CAROLINE DELANY as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Mozambique; KEVIN REX as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Lithuania, with residence in Riga; JASON TOLLAND as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Finland; and DAVID USHER as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Argentine Republic, with concurrent accreditation as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Paraguay, with residence in Buenos Aires.
